        {
            "title": "〈熱門股〉5月最飆股 禾伸堂噴漲201%傲視上市個股 創26年新高價",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"MLCC\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:MLCC;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/MLCC\">MLCC</a> 廠禾伸堂 (3026-TW) 在被動元件族群點火，5 月股價狂飆，單月大漲 201%、收 641 元創 26 年高；在上市個股中單月漲幅居冠，在上市櫃市場中也僅次於尚茂 (8291-TW) 的 444%，排名第二。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">被動元件近期受惠 AI 需求帶動拉貨動能強勁，尤其在高功率大電源應用，相關高階 MLCC 需求更為吃緊，禾伸堂董事長唐錦榮在近日股東會直言，市況從來沒有像今年那麼強，目前交期已拉長到 20 幾周，預計明年會更缺。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-085af3f7-7f00-33fb-9a59-b600b0635a1e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">唐錦榮進一步指出，今年輝達 (NVIDIA)(NVDA-US) Blackwell 仍是主要成長動能，新一代的 AI 伺服器平台 Vera Rubin 則預計第四季開始放量，MLCC 量價將進一步提升，因此預估明年營運會有更明顯的成長。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">從禾伸堂的籌碼面來看，三大法人 5 月同步站在買方，外資買超 6328 張、投信買超 1.2 萬張、自營商買超 65 張，合計買超 1.84 萬張，也推升股價走強；而禾伸堂今年前 5 月累計已上漲 528%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"禾伸堂日 K 線圖\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.F_sM5io_rctsNTfCLa6BQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/cnyes_hk_559/28e7e37494b43ab89b31e5a0bdb9cedb\" width=\"580\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:580px\">禾伸堂日 K 線圖</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap read-more-vendor break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>更多鉅亨報導</span><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"董座：MLCC市況從來沒有那麼好 今、明年各擴產約3成\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:董座：MLCC市況從來沒有那麼好 今、明年各擴產約3成;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6469769?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">董座：MLCC市況從來沒有那麼好 今、明年各擴產約3成</a><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"被動元件廠4月營收報佳音 國巨續創單月新高 禾伸堂寫4年最佳\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:被動元件廠4月營收報佳音 國巨續創單月新高 禾伸堂寫4年最佳;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6447787?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">被動元件廠4月營收報佳音 國巨續創單月新高 禾伸堂寫4年最佳</a></p></div>",
