        {
            "title": "〈熱門股〉矽晶圓全面復甦 環球晶週漲41% 躋身新千金",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"環球晶\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:環球晶;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/環球晶\">環球晶</a> (6488-TW) 本周召開股東會，董事長<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"徐秀蘭\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:徐秀蘭;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/徐秀蘭\">徐秀蘭</a>指出，現階段不僅 12 吋矽晶圓維持滿載，小尺寸也逐步拉升，同時也因應成本增加，全面性跟客戶討論新價格，在市場預期漲價帶動下，本周股價直線上升、最高達 1,020 元，創下歷史新高價、成為新千金，週五終場收在 1015 元，單周大漲 41.56%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">徐秀蘭坦言，過去經驗通常是產能先滿，再來才反映價格。去年因需求較弱，不敢跟客戶提漲價，今年因需求較滿，加上能源、油價、電費、勞工成本與通膨等成本上升，環球晶已積極與客戶溝通價格。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-fa88e745-24dc-39ca-a2a3-7a1b95575220-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">徐秀蘭補充，目前環球晶已全面性與客戶溝通價格，但不同規格、不同客戶、不同交易條件，調整幅度都不一樣。她指出，上半年多數價格已在去年第四季談完，因此目前希望下半年能看到一點改善。外界也對此解讀，隨著矽晶圓有望漲價，產業將迎來正向循環。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">環球晶本周沿五日線上攻，週四最高達 1,020 元，週五則中場則收在漲停板 1,015 元，單周成交量暴增至 8.4 萬張，不過，三大法人呈現土洋對作，外資小幅調節 1,657 張，投信與自營商則分別敲進 7,798 張、248 張。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"環球晶日 K 線圖\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Fr6s8hCsUVGfgsQLEKyV2g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/e35fc8f68273d6f8796cc0df75fb1f66\" width=\"580\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:580px\">環球晶日 K 線圖</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap read-more-vendor break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>更多鉅亨報導</span><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"12吋方形矽晶圓「磨」刀霍霍 均豪、東台成大贏家\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:12吋方形矽晶圓「磨」刀霍霍 均豪、東台成大贏家;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6469960?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">12吋方形矽晶圓「磨」刀霍霍 均豪、東台成大贏家</a><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"徐秀蘭：今年需求全面復甦 美國廠電費成本比預期高2成\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:徐秀蘭：今年需求全面復甦 美國廠電費成本比預期高2成;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6469937?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">徐秀蘭：今年需求全面復甦 美國廠電費成本比預期高2成</a></p></div>",
